snippet.title: District Steel - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
District Steel is out in Early Access, right NOW! Check it out!  
https://store.steampowered.com/app/616820/District_Steel/
   
District Steel is a full locomotion VR action game, inspired by the FPS classics. Blast your way through the underground SenTRI facility, equipped with a mechanical arm that gives time bending powers and a selection of deadly weapons.
   
©2023 - Barricade Studio 
http://www.barricadestudio.com
Music by Jorno
https://www.jornomusic.nl

#vr #gaming #steam
